{
  "stem": "10098.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 49.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Duke is not a Nazi, and all that stuff, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't hear anything more, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The world got to learn how cruelty, what can occur in a civilization, in a modern civilization-- Germany-- they called themselves the superior race-- what can happen to human beings, how people can turn to barbarism, to something which it's not heard in this 20th century civilization, people can do one human to another on.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, especially Jews, we got to remind people what could happen, what can happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we need to be on the top, and remind people, and teach the children about the cruelty for one person, what he did to the world, what he did especially to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And building the [? all ?] Holocaust museums and the whole thing, I think that's a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot just sweep that under the rug.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You've got to remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And especially our people, we have to remember what happened to our people, how the people shouldn't be buried somewhere in vain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We should remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we do remember-- myself, as long as I'm alive, the good Lord keep me alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we have memorial services.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we always remember the people who perish, people who never did nobody anything, people who were innocent people-- children, women, all the people who got murdered by the Nazi.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we've got to see something like this should never happen again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's up to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we got to teach the people, and talk about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people got to be informed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think Mr.-- all the movies, what's going on, that Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Spielberg doing a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They're doing something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Let the people-- a lot of people say, I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't realize what happened to people and the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People have got to know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The same people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When I meet people and talk to people what happened, how during the bitter years, and the Nazi-- under the Nazis' rule in Germany, people don't really realize.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They thought only Jews were murdered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were other kinds of nationalities were murdered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "People got to know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was a concentration camp with Catholic, Protestants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were murdered, too, by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and any dictatorship, you know, have to be checked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And see, something like this should never happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it's up to the people, and to the world, to the free people to teach each other nations what cruelty and what racism, bigotry can happen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my wife Tola and myself, our wedding picture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Germany we took that picture-- November 11, 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And who's in this picture?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is Tola and myself, presently pictured.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, we'd been celebrating after our anniversary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945-- 1995.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Taken in a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Monroe, Louisiana.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my wife, Tola, in the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's my girlfriend-- TOLA ROSENBERG (WIFE): [CHUCKLING] --for many, many years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hope to live to celebrate our next diamond anniversary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just present-- recently, we celebrated our 50, our golden anniversary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is my long-life girlfriend, Tola-- the blondie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] That's who I was introduced first time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My friend told me, I want you to meet one of the best-looking girls in town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "TOLA ROSENBERG (WIFE): [CHUCKLING]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
